---
import fs from 'node:fs';
import path from 'node:path';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/about.css';

const signaturePath = path.resolve('./public/parker-signature.svg');
const signatureSvg = fs.readFileSync(signaturePath, 'utf-8')
  .replace(/<\?xml[^?]*\?>/, '')
  .replace(/<!DOCTYPE[^>]*>/, '');
---
<Layout title="About — Parker Tikson" description="A longer answer to so what do you do — how Parker Tikson got into energy systems work, and the things outside it that make it possible.">

  <header class="about-header">
    <h1>The longer answer to “so what do you do?”</h1>
  </header>

  <article class="letter">
    <p class="placeholder-note">
      <em>A longer letter is coming. I'm sitting with how to say it well. For now, the work, the photographs, and the résumé carry most of what I'd want you to know.</em>
    </p>

    <div class="signoff">
      <p>With warmth,</p>
      <div class="sig" aria-label="Parker's signature" set:html={signatureSvg} />
    </div>
  </article>

  <section class="connect">
    <p>If any of this resonates, I'd love to hear from you.</p>
    <p class="actions">
      <a href="mailto:parkertikson@gmail.com">Email</a>
      <span class="sep"> · </span>
      <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/parkertikson/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
    </p>
  </section>

</Layout>
